{"tid":930824,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"候夫諷剌費蘭尼：睇黎我教得你唔錯","createTime":"2018-12-06T14:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T00:58:27.000Z","uid":124292,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b511b265e48b93e6ce93e0af028cc38c5e7d7d06","tid":930824,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T14:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WefEzNz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWefEzNz.png&h=d3e2880f&s={SIZE}\" />曼聯2-2戰平阿仙奴的比賽中，曼聯中場費蘭尼在一次防守中扯了阿仙奴中場古安杜斯的頭髮，他的這個行為也遭到了前李斯特城中堅候夫的嘲諷。<br />\n<br />\n事實上早在2016年曼聯對陣李斯特斯的比賽，候夫就曾經在防守中扯了費蘭尼的頭髮，隨後費蘭尼直接抬起手肘回擊了候夫，比賽結束後兩人都被禁賽了3場比賽。<br />\n<br />\n胡候夫到了費蘭尼的扯頭髮的行為之後，在推特上寫道：「看樣子我教你教得不錯。」"},{"pid":"448067e6f2427d166c323c024cc99513ff8ff5c7","tid":930824,"uid":5649,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8533a53db9e563aa9d241c0e3734b022c6ffa4ef","tid":930824,"uid":194877,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"448067e6f2427d166c323c024cc99513ff8ff5c7","tid":930824,"uid":5649,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"人先有資格撚狗<br />\nE 家擺明狗咬狗"},{"pid":"f318ff1b6f81f5d03b8e18e552b5022647966fc4","tid":930824,"uid":5649,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"8533a53db9e563aa9d241c0e3734b022c6ffa4ef","tid":930824,"uid":194877,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"448067e6f2427d166c323c024cc99513ff8ff5c7","tid":930824,"uid":5649,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass